OL,3,CStarmer unveils #1 billion French and
OL,4,CIndian investments at G7
OL,6,FFrench and Indian companies will pour
OL,7,F#1.3 billion into clean energy and AI
OL,8,Fprojects in the UK, Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fhas said at the G7 summit.
OL,11,FThe investment will bring more than
OL,12,F1,400 jobs to Manchester, Leeds and
OL,13,FBirmingham.
OL,15,FIt includes #1 billion from French
OL,16,Fprivate equity firm InfraVia for
OL,17,Fbattery storage and a flexible energy
OL,18,Fplatform that can be switched on to
OL,19,Fboost supply when renewable energy is
OL,20,Flow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
