OL,3,CStarmer unveils #1 billion French and
OL,4,CIndian investments at G7
OL,6,FAnother #25 million will come from
OL,7,FIndia's Hexaware Technologies and #300
OL,8,Fmillion from Atri Energy Transition to
OL,9,Fdevelop large-scale battery storage.
OL,11,FSir Keir said: "The world is more
OL,12,Fdangerous than it has been for a
OL,13,Fgeneration, with conflict abroad
OL,14,Fwashing up on our shores.
OL,16,F"That's why I'm focused on making the
OL,17,FUK the best place to do business by
OL,18,Foffering global investors the
OL,19,Fstability and competitive environment
OL,20,Fthey need to grow, even in the face of
OL,21,Fglobal uncertainty.
