OL,3,CStarmer unveils #1 billion French and
OL,4,CIndian investments at G7
OL,6,F"These investments will create
OL,7,Fthousands of high-skilled jobs, back
OL,8,FBritish innovation and strengthen our
OL,9,Fenergy system so families are better
OL,10,Fprotected from global shocks."
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister is working with G7
OL,13,Fpartners to ease pressures on global
OL,14,Fenergy markets, including efforts to
OL,15,Fstabilise key shipping routes and de-
OL,16,Fescalate tensions in the Middle East
OL,17,Fto help bring down costs for
OL,18,Fhouseholds.
